<div id="instructions">
<div id="instructionscontainer">
<button id="show_instructions">What is this?</button>
<div id="hidden_instructions">
  <p>
  Sometimes we get carried away with the big 'important' things in life and forget how
  many happy minutes and seconds we have had.
  </p>
  <p>
  <strong>This is your happiness jar.</strong> Use it to keep track of every bubble bath you
  take, every puppy you pet. Use it to retrieve sweetness when you're a bit
  sour.
  </p>
  <p>
  Give us your <strong>phone number</strong> and we'll store every text you send us in your
  jar. Give us your <strong>email address</strong> and at the end of the year happy memories will fill
  your inbox.
  </p>
  <p>
  And of course, a silly quote on the topic from Simon and Garfunkel:
  <strong>"I've got nothing to do today but smile."</strong>
  </p>
  <button class="close">close</button>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

